{"hash":"f60f81fcd5a11bef756902ea798e1e190db10bbe","data":{"page":{"title":"Provider - Gist","content":"<h2 id=\"configuration\"><a href=\"#configuration\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Configuration</h2>\n<p>There is no configuration for this provider.</p>\n<h2 id=\"examples\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Examples</h2>\n<h3 id=\"show-only-a-specific-file\"><a href=\"#show-only-a-specific-file\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Show only a specific file</h3>\n<p>To show only one file, you can use the following syntax inside your markdown file:</p>\n<div class=\"gridsome-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">https://gist.github.com/&lt;user&gt;/&lt;gistid&gt;#file1.js\nor\nhttps://gist.github.com/&lt;user&gt;/&lt;gistid&gt;?file=file1.js</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"code-highlighting\"><a href=\"#code-highlighting\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Code Highlighting</h3>\n<p>To highlight one or more lines in a gist file, you can use the following syntax inside your markdown file:</p>\n<div class=\"gridsome-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">https://gist.github.com/&lt;user&gt;/&lt;gistid&gt;?file=file1.js&amp;highlights=1,3,5-10,15-20</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"external-assets\"><a href=\"#external-assets\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>External Assets</h2>\n<p>By default, the plugin does not append or load external assets, you have to add the following resources manually.</p>\n<div class=\"gridsome-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">https://github.githubassets.com/assets/gist-embed-d89dc96f3ab6372bb73ee45cafdd0711.css</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-your-own-asset-url\"><a href=\"#get-your-own-asset-url\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Get your own asset url</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Create a new <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">github gist</a></li>\n<li>Add <code class=\"language-text\">.json</code> to the gist url e.g. <code class=\"language-text\">https://gist.github.com/&lt;yourgithubname&gt;/&lt;gistid&gt;.json</code></li>\n<li>Search for <code class=\"language-text\">stylesheet</code></li>\n<li>Copy the url</li>\n</ol>\n"},"repo":{"title":"Remark Embed","content":"<p>Gridsome Remark plugin to embed external stuff into your gridsome site.</p>\n","repository":"noxify/gridsome-plugin-remark-embed"},"sidebar":{"edges":[{"node":{"category":[{"id":"bd42a8b6","title":"Getting started","links":[{"id":"589a0909","title":"Introduction","url":""},{"id":"5a6ba485","title":"Custom Template","url":"/custom-template"}]},{"id":"ceb5c264","title":"Provider","links":[{"id":"673405f2","title":"Codepen","url":"/provider-codepen"},{"id":"632485a8","title":"Codesandbox","url":"/provider-codesandbox"},{"id":"3ab64b40","title":"Facebook Post","url":"/provider-facebook-post"},{"id":"6a0cad80","title":"Facebook Video","url":"/provider-facebook-video"},{"id":"250b017d","title":"Giphy","url":"/provider-giphy"},{"id":"7ef2e9e0","title":"Gist","url":"/provider-gist"},{"id":"c2aab992","title":"JSFiddle","url":"/provider-jsfiddle"},{"id":"7eae7463","title":"Soundcloud","url":"/provider-soundcloud"},{"id":"17cf2214","title":"Spotify","url":"/provider-spotify"},{"id":"76eb4738","title":"Twitter","url":"/provider-twitter"},{"id":"7799b3c9","title":"Vimeo","url":"/provider-vimeo"},{"id":"0729519c","title":"Youtube","url":"/provider-youtube"}]}]}}]}},"context":{"id":"d85978680a3207861b9ff6fadea77ace","plugin":"gridsome-plugin-remark-embed","pluginId":"gridsome-plugin-remark-embed"}}